resources.string: "Íoslódáil gnéithe breise do Chlúdach Amhairc LED agus suiteáil iad. Is féidir leat íocóin LED de do chuid féin a chruthú agus iad a shocrú mar d'íocóin fógra. Lena n-íoslódáil ar ball, gabh chuig Socruithe > Ardghnéithe > Oiriúintí > Clúdach Amhairc LED, ansin roghnaigh Íoslódáil gnéithe breise."

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
